ANN In-Depth is a live discussion and commentary program hosted by Jennifer Stymiest and Sam Neves of the General Conference Communication Department. Each day at 12:30pm and 8pm, we’ll take you inside GC Session and breakdown the days decisions.

ANN Website: https://adventist.news/
ANN Twitter: https://twitter.com/adventistnews
